high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the kitchen island.
Pick up the leftmost white plate off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left again and walk up to the oven and look up.
Put the white plate in the microwave and microwave it for a couple seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost big upper cabinet door and put the heated plate inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated white plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the plate closest to you from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Heat up the plate in the microwave and then pick up the plate from the microwave.
Walk to the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
Place the plate inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved plate inside the cabinet to the right of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter.
Turn around and look up at the microwave above the stove.
Step to the right and look up at the cabinet next to the microwave.
Place the plate in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm plate in the cabinet.
